B is -[C(R1)(R2)n-R3 wherein

n is an integer between 1 and 10,

R1 and R2 represent independently in each of the n units a substituent selected from the group consisting of hydrogen, substituted or not C1-C10 alkyl, halogen, oxy derivatives, thio derivatives, substituted or not C3-C10 cycloalkyl, substituted or not C6-C18 aryl, subtituted or not C2-C10 alkenyl, and subtituted or not C2-C10 alkynyl;

